fields.name: Alpine Drive Mansionette
fields.description: Extraordinary scale, soaring ceilings and natural light embody this newer contemporary oasis. Perfectly situated on a sprawling northern lot in the 500 block of the highly coveted Alpine Drive, this 6,500 square foot estate boasts grand entertaining spaces, 6 generous bedrooms, and an expansive upstairs family room, dedicated office, gym, entertaining bar, breakfast nook, indoor water feature, and stunning walnut staircase.

fields.name: 4 bedfroom Country House
fields.description: Carriage Drive is found on a delightful and quiet backwater within Littleborough, accessed via a private lane offering superb privacy with the grounds not being overlooked. Though the property offers such tranquillity it is far from isolated being within walking distance of Littleborough town centre and its array of amenities which include a train station offering ease of access to both Leeds and Manchester.

fields.name: 7 bedroom Norfolk House
fields.description: Wilby Hall is a significant late 16th century part moated country house, Grade II Listed and wonderfully positioned at the heart of its own 12 acres of mature gardens and grounds. The house is architecturally distinguished, built of mellow red brick with crow stepped gables, mullioned and transomed windows which retain much of the original glass, and fine internal period detail.

fields.name: Hereford Mansion
fields.description: A magnificent Georgian House with fine landscaped gardens and lake at the heart of an idyllic country estate. Coach House, Victorian stable block, manege and paddocks, beautiful restored productive walled garden, 11 flats, cottages and farmhouses, parkland and woodland, working farms.

fields.name: Charmilon Lane Mansion
fields.description: Exquisite Custom Gated Contemporary Estate in prime Encino.  Amazing View lot with jetliner views.  Over 11,000 sqft of luxury living on ¾ of an acre.  6 luxury en suite bedrooms, 10 bathrooms all with the finest finishes and perfection of design.  The grand living room boasts a floating staircase, ceilings soaring over 30+ ft with a wall of windows overlooking the San Fernando Valley. Incredible open floor plan. Sumptuous master suite is a 1500

fields.name: Amalfi Drive Castle
fields.description: A spectacular Mediterranean estate on almost 1/2 acre in the Riviera. Exquisite craftsmanship, dramatic 2-story entry with wood-beam ceiling, French doors throughout, 3 fireplaces, limestone floors, crown molding, wine cellar, center hall plan with 5 bedroom suites. Master with fireplace, his & hers marble baths, gym, sitting room, or guest suite with separate entrance.

fields.name: Beverly Drive Mansion
fields.address: 1021 N. BEVERLY DR., BEVERLY HILLS, CA 90210
fields.description: A sprawling Beverly Hills contemporary estate on over 1 acre of land, recently completed with meticulous attention to design and detail. Developed by Sen Properties, the 7 beds, 10 baths main residence boasts 15,605 sq. ft. of stylish living spaces including an elegant foyer, top-of-the-line chef’s kitchen, sleek dining and living areas, state-of-the-art movie theater and gym, wine cellar, a lavish owner’s suite with his-and-hers walk-in closets

fields.name: Meadowgate Mansion
fields.description: An exquisite 9,200+ sq. ft. estate set on nearly a half-acre of land in the prime Royal Oaks neighborhood of Encino. Features 5 en-suite bedrooms and 7 bathrooms with European craftsmanship throughout, including walnut hardwood floors, custom wall coverings and Venetian plaster ceilings. Incredible professional chef's kitchen with Carrara marble counters and backsplash, walk-in pantry and breakfast bar, all leading to the magnificent great room.

fields.name: Sydney Beachside Mansion
fields.address: 25 Thyra Road Sydney, New South Wales, 2108 Australia
fields.description: urrounded by nature, this superb lifestyle property offers more a way of life than simply a place to stay, and represents a rare opportunity to witness a slice of paradise and become a part of a privileged beachside enclave in one of Palm Beach's most sought-after positions.

fields.name: Castillo Caribe
fields.description: Castillo Caribe offers a rare opportunity to combine this with privacy, security, luxury and lifestyle all on a pristine white sandy beach overlooking the crystal clear waters of the Caribbean Sea.

fields.name: The White House
fields.description: There are 132 rooms, 35 bathrooms, and 6 levels in the Residence. There are also 412 doors, 147 windows, 28 fireplaces, 8 staircases, and 3 elevators.The White House kitchen is able to serve dinner to as many as 140 guests and hors d'oeuvres to more than 1,000. The White House requires 570 gallons of paint to cover its outside surface.

fields.name: Tha Dogg House
fields.description: The rap legend's mansion is located in the gated community of County Estates; a supposedly middle-class suburb that sits on a cul-de-sac. The house takes up 2.8 acres of land, having a square footage of 4,000. Sources reported that the mansion has 4 beds and 4 baths, as well as a pool and spa area, as well as a basketball court. The estate is said to be full of panoramic views at every angle. The mansion sounds like everyone's dream house.

fields.name: Kensington Town House
fields.description: The refurbishment this Grade ll listed detached 1862 Stucco house in Kensington has started on site.

fields.name: Laurelwood Drive Mansion
fields.description: The newly-built Studio City retreat featured on season two and three, and was hard to shift mainly due to its steeply sloping driveway and lack of car parking space. Situated on a secluded plot behind private gates, the ultra-secure home is entirely bespoke and benefits from high-end interior design and custom finishes throughout.

fields.name: Beckham Manor House
fields.description: It"s easy to see why the family spend so much time there; as well as having stunning interiors with log-burning fires and exposed brick walls, the country retreat has incredible gardens with a pool, tennis court and sauna.

fields.name: Paris Town House
fields.description: In a prestigious, calm and secure district of the 16th arrondissement of Paris, on a closed square, stands behind a historic facade, a newly built and inimitable 1,237 sqm property. This house contains an extremely comfortable interior with the best of the latest modern features, pleasant volumes and nice large windows allowing natural light in, just like the original glass roof.

fields.name: Luxury Swiss Chalet
fields.description: Located away from prying eyes, in the heart of the village, a few steps from the ski slopes and at the end of a private road, the Chalet Fleur des Neiges dominates with a breathtaking view of the Dents du Midi chain.

fields.name: Extraordinary German Villa
fields.description: In the sought-after district of Ammerland, on a sun-drenched plot of land directly at Lake Starnberg, a prestigious manor house is for sale that offers the best conditions for fulfilling long-cherished life and living dreams. A historical villa with about 375 sqm living space and about 137 sqm usable area awaits you, which is embedded in a secluded park property with flowering hedges, large trees, comfortable outdoor seats and well-kept English lawns.

fields.name: Belmont Estate
fields.description: From the very arrival, the porte-cochère entrance and stone waterfall are part of the detailing that create the exceptional experience that one has from being here. Dramatic, solid oak cathedral doors flank the home"s entrance, you find yourself standing still in the grand hallway where light, glass, art, and soaring ceilings prevail over any expectations. You understand the display that this room offers, which among many things contains a striking French Ormolu chandelier, a grand piano and grand hall which has been played in by world class musicians.

fields.name: Santiago"s Most Exclusive Property
fields.description: Exclusive property of the renowned architect De Groote in the top of Lo Curro neighbourhood, with an impressive panoramic view that dominates the city strip and mountain range. An imposing access flanked by large palm trees leads to the property´s entrance which receives visitors with it´s wonderful carved wooden doors. Distribution hall with marble floor and wooden marquetry, leads to the elegant living room with parquet floors, high ceilings, upholstered walls and vaulted ceilings with hand-painted wood.

fields.name: Atelier House
fields.description: Atelier House is a stunning Caribbean retreat. The design was conceptualised in close collaboration with the interior architect / owner, who has completed projects for discerning homeowners in London, France, Italy and Kenya. The dramatic double-height living space maximizes the stunning views which extend beyond the outdoor terraces and pool across a mahogany tree-filled gully to the Caribbean Sea. In addition to the ground-level terraces and 32 x 27 ft. pool there is a large roof terrace and mezzanine-level study offering stunning views of the West Coast.

fields.name: Coin de Mire Gate Villa
fields.description: This stunning seven-bedroom luxury beachfront villa overlooking the nature reserve islet, Coin de Mire, offers the ultimate luxurious island lifestyle.The beautifully appointed open plan ground floor living area opens out entirely to a landscaped garden and pool deck with a jacuzzi and water feature. Relax on a lounger on balmy summer days and watch the boats sail past or stroll across the grass verge and dive into the azure ocean.

fields.name: Point Piper
fields.description: First time offered in 20 years. It is unique, it is unrivalled. A Residence of inspiration and unsurpassed grandeur. Breathtakingly executed to a finite degree. Set in a private oasis right on Seven Shillings Beach. Back dropped by idyllic Bay & Harbour views from the beach to the Opera House, Harbour Bridge and beyond. Accompanied by Sydney's most coveted 'Pagoda' Boathouse and calm, deepwater berth for year round mooring. This masterpiece of residential architecture, designed by Richard Christian and Walter Barda, indulges every possible personal extravagance, need, whim and necessity.

fields.name: Karuizawa Residence
fields.description: This unique Japanese home is the swap for you. It"s absolutely huge and has a massive wine celler for you to get drunk with all your mates.

fields.name: Moscow Penthouse
fields.description: Luxury apartments are located on the 69th floor of Federation Towers. Platinum apartments - from the 91st floor. Penthouse occupies 95-97 floors. At this height, exceptional views - only the sky around you. According to the international classification of skyscrapers "Federation Tower" is an ultra-high skyscraper - its height is 374 meters. Real panoramic windows - from wall to wall, from floor to ceiling, without bars and handrails. Nothing prevents you from enjoying the stunning lively paintings of Moscow.
